config = resnet_model.get_config()
classifier = KerasGClassifier(config, model_type='functional')
params = {'layers_1_Conv2D__config__kernel_initializer__config__seed': 9999,
    'layers_1_Conv2D__config__filters': 64, 'lr': 0.03, 'epochs': 200}
classifier.set_params(**params)
got1 = classifier.config['layers'][1]['config']['kernel_initializer']['config'
    ]['seed']
got2 = classifier.config['layers'][1]['config']['filters']
got3 = classifier.lr
got4 = classifier.epochs
assert got1 == 9999, got1
assert got2 == 64, got2
assert got3 == 0.03, got3
assert got4 == 200, got4
